| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4798 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 02e1f037-6851-5746-9ff8-5eaf3e2f651a"
